      "prompt": "请创建一个完整的 HTML5 游戏。游戏描述：创建一个太空射击游戏。\n                    \n重要技术要求：\n1. 单个 HTML 文件\n2. 使用 Canvas API\n3. Canvas 尺寸必须为 360x640 像素（9:16 竖屏比例）\n4. 在 JavaScript 中设置：canvas.width = 360; canvas.height = 640;\n5. 在 CSS 中设置：canvas { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n6. 包含完整游戏循环\n7. 有得分系统\n8. 确保有趣可玩\n\n只返回 HTML 代码，不要其他说明。",
      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>太空射击游戏</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        #gameContainer {\n            position: relative;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        canvas {\n            display: block;\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        #uiOverlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        \n        #scoreDisplay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 20px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        #scoreValue {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            margin-left: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        #highScoreDisplay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n        \n        .menuScreen {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            pointer-events: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .menuTitle {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        .menuButton {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5 0%, #38b2ac 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 15px 40px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.4);\n            pointer-events: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .menuButton:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.6);\n        }\n        \n        .instructions {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        \n        .hidden {\n            display: none !important;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"gameContainer\">\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"360\" height=\"640\"></canvas>\n        <div id=\"uiOverlay\">\n            <div id=\"scoreDisplay\">得分: <span id=\"scoreValue\">0</span></div>\n            <div id=\"highScoreDisplay\">最高分: <span id=\"highScoreValue\">0</span></div>\n            \n            <!-- 主菜单 -->\n            <div id=\"mainMenu\" class=\"menuScreen\">\n                <div class=\"menuTitle\">太空射击</div>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"startButton\">开始游戏</button>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"pauseResumeButton\" style=\"display: none;\">继续游戏</button>\n                <div class=\"instructions\">\n                    操作说明：<br>\n                    ← → 或 A/D：移动飞船<br>\n                    空格键：射击<br>\n                    P键：暂停游戏\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 暂停菜单 -->\n            <div id=\"pauseMenu\" class=\"menuScreen hidden\">\n                <div class=\"menuTitle\">游戏暂停</div>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"resumeButton\">继续游戏</button>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"restartFromPauseButton\">重新开始</button>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 游戏结束菜单 -->\n            <div id=\"gameOverMenu\" class=\"menuScreen hidden\">\n                <div class=\"menuTitle\">游戏结束</div>\n                <div style=\"color: white; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    最终得分: <span id=\"finalScore\" style=\"color: #4fd1c5;\">0</span>\n                </div>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"restartButton\">重新开始</button>\n                <button class=\"menuButton\" id=\"mainMenuButton\">返回主菜单</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 游戏常量\n        const CANVAS_WIDTH = 360;\n        const CANVAS_HEIGHT = 640;\n        const PLAYER_SPEED = 300;\n        const BULLET_SPEED = 500;\n        const ENEMY_SPEED = 150;\n        const ENEMY_SPAWN_RATE = 0.02;\n        \n        // 游戏状态\n        const GameState = {\n            MENU: 'menu',\n            PLAYING: 'playing',\n            PAUSED: 'paused',\n            GAMEOVER: 'gameover'\n        };\n        \n        // 游戏变量\n        let canvas, ctx;\n        let gameState = GameState.MENU;\n        let score = 0;\n        let highScore = 0;\n        let lastTime = 0;\n        let player, bullets, enemies;\n        let keys = {};\n        let shootCooldown = 0;\n        const SHOOT_COOLDOWN_TIME = 0.2;\n        \n        // 初始化游戏\n        function init() {\n            canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\n            ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n            \n            // 加载最高分\n            highScore = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('spaceShooterHighScore')) || 0;\n            document.getElementById('highScoreValue').textContent = highScore;\n            \n            // 初始化游戏对象\n            resetGame();\n            \n            // 设置事件监听器\n            setupEventListeners();\n            \n            // 开始游戏循环\n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 重置游戏\n        function resetGame() {\n            score = 0;\n            document.getElementById('scoreValue').textContent = score;\n            \n            // 初始化玩家\n            player = {\n                x: CANVAS_WIDTH / 2 - 20,\n                y: CANVAS_HEIGHT - 80,\n                width: 40,\n                height: 40,\n                color: '#4fd1c5'\n            };\n            \n            // 初始化数组\n            bullets = [];\n            enemies = [];\n            shootCooldown = 0;\n        }\n        \n        // 设置事件监听器\n        function setupEventListeners() {\n            // 键盘事件\n            document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {\n                keys[e.code] = true;\n                handleInput(e.code, true);\n            });\n            \n            document.addEventListener('keyup', (e) => {\n                keys[e.code] = false;\n                handleInput(e.code, false);\n            });\n            \n            // 按钮事件\n            document.getElementById('startButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('pauseResumeButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('resumeButton').addEventListener('click', resumeGame);\n            document.getElementById('restartFromPauseButton').addEventListener('click', restartGame);\n            document.getElementById('restartButton').addEventListener('click', restartGame);\n            document.getElementById('mainMenuButton').addEventListener('click', goToMainMenu);\n        }\n        \n        // 开始游戏\n        function startGame() {\n            gameState = GameState.PLAYING;\n            document.getElementById('mainMenu').classList.add('hidden');\n            document.getElementById('pauseMenu').classList.add('hidden');\n            document.getElementById('gameOverMenu').classList.add('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 恢复游戏\n        function resumeGame() {\n            gameState = GameState.PLAYING;\n            document.getElementById('pauseMenu').classList.add('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 重新开始游戏\n        function restartGame() {\n            resetGame();\n            startGame();\n        }\n        \n        // 返回主菜单\n        function goToMainMenu() {\n            gameState = GameState.MENU;\n            document.getElementById('gameOverMenu').classList.add('hidden');\n            document.getElementById('mainMenu').classList.remove('hidden');\n            document.getElementById('pauseResumeButton').style.display = 'inline-block';\n        }\n        \n        // 输入处理\n        function handleInput(key, pressed) {\n            if (key === 'KeyP' && pressed) {\n                if (gameState === GameState.PLAYING) {\n                    gameState = GameState.PAUSED;\n                    document.getElementById('pauseMenu').classList.remove('hidden');\n                } else if (gameState === GameState.PAUSED) {\n                    resumeGame();\n                }\n            }\n            \n            if (key === 'Space' && pressed && gameState === GameState.PLAYING) {\n                shoot();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 射击\n        function shoot() {\n            if (shootCooldown <= 0) {\n                bullets.push({\n                    x: player.x + player.width / 2 - 3,\n                    y: player.y,\n                    width: 6,\n                    height: 15,\n                    color: '#ff6b6b'\n                });\n                shootCooldown = SHOOT_COOLDOWN_TIME;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 生成敌人\n        function spawnEnemy() {\n            if (Math.random() < ENEMY_SPAWN_RATE) {\n                const enemyWidth = 30 + Math.random() * 20;\n                const enemyHeight = 30 + Math.random() * 20;\n                enemies.push({\n                    x: Math.random() * (CANVAS_WIDTH - enemyWidth),\n                    y: -enemyHeight,\n                    width: enemyWidth,\n                    height: enemyHeight,\n                    color: '#ff9f43',\n                    speed: ENEMY_SPEED + Math.random() * 100\n                });\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏循环\n        function gameLoop(currentTime) {\n            const deltaTime = (currentTime - lastTime) / 1000;\n            lastTime = currentTime;\n            \n            if (gameState === GameState.PLAYING) {\n                update(deltaTime);\n            }\n            \n            render();\n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 更新游戏逻辑\n        function update(deltaTime) {\n            // 更新射击冷却\n            if (shootCooldown > 0) {\n                shootCooldown -= deltaTime;\n            }\n            \n            // 更新玩家位置\n            if (keys['ArrowLeft'] || keys['KeyA']) {\n                player.x -= PLAYER_SPEED * deltaTime;\n            }\n            if (keys['ArrowRight'] || keys['KeyD']) {\n                player.x += PLAYER_SPEED * deltaTime;\n            }\n            \n            // 限制玩家在屏幕内\n            player.x = Math.max(0, Math.min(CANVAS_WIDTH - player.width, player.x));\n            \n            // 更新子弹\n            for (let i = bullets.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n                bullets[i].y -= BULLET_SPEED * deltaTime;\n                if (bullets[i].y + bullets[i].height < 0) {\n                    bullets.splice(i, 1);\n                }\n            }\n            \n            // 生成敌人\n            spawnEnemy();\n            \n            // 更新敌人\n            for (let i = enemies.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n                enemies[i].y += enemies[i].speed * deltaTime;\n                \n                // 敌人到达底部\n                if (enemies[i].y > CANVAS_HEIGHT) {\n                    enemies.splice(i, 1);\n                    continue;\n                }\n                \n                // 检测子弹与敌人碰撞\n                for (let j = bullets.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {\n                    if (checkCollision(bullets[j], enemies[i])) {\n                        // 击中敌人\n                        score += 10;\n                        document.getElementById('scoreValue').textContent = score;\n                        enemies.splice(i, 1);\n                        bullets.splice(j, 1);\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n                \n                // 检测玩家与敌人碰撞\n                if (enemies[i] && checkCollision(player, enemies[i])) {\n                    gameOver();\n                    return;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 检测碰撞\n        function checkCollision(rect1, rect2) {\n            return rect1.x < rect2.x + rect2.width &&\n                   rect1.x + rect1.width > rect2.x &&\n                   rect1.y < rect2.y + rect2.height &&\n                   rect1.y + rect1.height > rect2.y;\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏结束\n        function gameOver() {\n            gameState = GameState.GAMEOVER;\n            \n            // 更新最高分\n            if (score > highScore) {\n                highScore = score;\n                localStorage.setItem('spaceShooterHighScore', highScore);\n                document.getElementById('highScoreValue').textContent = highScore;\n            }\n            \n            document.getElementById('finalScore').textContent = score;\n            document.getElementById('gameOverMenu').classList.remove('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 渲染游戏\n        function render() {\n            // 清空画布\n            ctx.clearRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制背景\n            const gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            gradient.addColorStop(0, '#1a1a2e');\n            gradient.addColorStop(1, '#16213e');\n            ctx.fillStyle = gradient;\n            ctx.fillRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制星星背景\n            drawStars();\n            \n            if (gameState === GameState.PLAYING || gameState === GameState.PAUSED) {\n                // 绘制玩家\n                drawPlayer();\n                \n                // 绘制子弹\n                drawBullets();\n                \n                // 绘制敌人\n                drawEnemies();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制星星背景\n        function drawStars() {\n            ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)';\n            for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) {\n                const x = (Math.sin(i * 0.5 + lastTime * 0.001) * 0.5 + 0.5) * CANVAS_WIDTH;\n                const y = (i * 13) % CANVAS_HEIGHT;\n                const size = (i % 3) + 1;\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(x, y, size, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制玩家\n        function drawPlayer() {\n            ctx.fillStyle = player.color;\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.moveTo(player.x + player.width / 2, player.y);\n            ctx.lineTo(player.x + player.width, player.y + player.height);\n            ctx.lineTo(player.x, player.y + player.height);\n            ctx.closePath();\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制引擎效果\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#ff6b6b';\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.moveTo(player.x + player.width / 2 - 5, player.y + player.height);\n            ctx.lineTo(player.x + player.width / 2 + 5, player.y + player.height);\n            ctx.lineTo(player.x + player.width / 2, player.y + player.height + 10);\n            ctx.closePath();\n            ctx.fill();\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制子弹\n        function drawBullets() {\n            bullets.forEach(bullet => {\n                ctx.fillStyle = bullet.color;\n                ctx.fillRect(bullet.x, bullet.y, bullet.width, bullet.height);\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 绘制敌人\n        function drawEnemies() {\n            enemies.forEach(enemy => {\n                ctx.fillStyle = enemy.color;\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x + enemy.width / 2, enemy.y + enemy.height / 2, enemy.width / 2, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制敌人细节\n                ctx.fillStyle = '#ee5a24';\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x + enemy.width / 2, enemy.y + enemy.height / 2, enemy.width / 4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 启动游戏\n        window.onload = init;\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
